snippet.title: Dodge Racer for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Dodge Racer is an action-racing game quite similar to Dodge 'Em, which was released for the Atari 2600.

You have to collect all dots, while avoiding the other racer.


What I think:

Okay game, but quite repetitive. Every level is like the first one, but with a smarter and faster opponent.
